{"article_id":"OHbnqvA5D7xqmnIh","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Former acting FBI Director Andrew McCabe said Sunday","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"that Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein was so serious about using the 25th Amendment","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"to oust President Trump ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"he was counting \" votes or possible votes \" among Cabinet members .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"In an interview with \" 60 Minutes \"","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"to promote his upcoming book ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Mr. McCabe said","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Mr. Rosenstein offered to wear a wire during his next meeting with Mr. Trump .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"The reason ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"Mr. McCabe said ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"was because Mr. Rosenstein wanted to learn the president ' s motivation","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"for firing former FBI Director James B. Comey in the early stages of what would ultimately become special counsel Robert Mueller ' s Russia collusion probe .","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"\" Now he was not joking , \"","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"Mr. McCabe said .","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"\" He was absolutely serious .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"And , in fact , he brought it up in the next meeting","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"we had .","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"I never actually considered taking him up on the offer . \"","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"The recording would have been to collect evidence","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"on whether Mr. Comey ' s firing amounted to obstruction of justice ,","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"according to Mr. McCabe .","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"When that idea was shot down ,","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Mr. McCabe said ,","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"Mr. Rosenstein discussed invoking the 25th Amendment .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"The amendment is a process","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"for the Cabinet","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"to force the removal of a president","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"they consider unable to perform the duties of the office .","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"\" To be fair ,","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"it was an unbelievably stressful time , \"","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"Mr. McCabe said .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"\" I can ' t even describe for you how many things must have been coursing through the deputy attorney general ' s mind at that point . \"","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"Mr. Rosenstein has called the allegations \" inaccurate and factually incorrect. \"","depth":3},{"id":33,"text":"Last fall , a Justice Department official dismissed a report in The New York Times","depth":4},{"id":34,"text":"claiming","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"Mr. Rosenstein offered to wear a wire as a joke .","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"On Sunday , Fox News reported","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"that top Justice Department lawyer James Baker testified before Congress in May","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"that Mr. McCabe and FBI lawyer Lisa Page told him","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"that Mr. Rosenstein was talking to high-ranking Trump administration officials","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"about ousting the president under the 25th Amendment .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"The discussions occurred in May 2017 , in the aftermath of Mr. Comey ' s abrupt firing ,","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"according to the report .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"Mr. Baker reportedly told lawmakers","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"that Rosenstein knew of at least two Cabinet officials","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"who would support the move .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"Mr. Baker also said","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"he did not believe","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"Mr. Rosenstein was joking .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"He told lawmakers ,","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"\" this was not a joking sort of time , \"","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"according to the Fox News report .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"Asked Sunday","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"if Mr. Rosenstein was \" openly talking \"","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"about whether Cabinet members supported the idea ,","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"Mr. McCabe said","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"the No . 2 official at the Justice Department was \" counting votes or possible votes . \"","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"Hours before the \" 60 Minutes \" interview , Senate Judiciary Committee Chairman Lindsey Graham pledged","depth":4},{"id":58,"text":"his panel will investigate the allegations","depth":5},{"id":59,"text":"Mr. Rosenstein sought to oust the president .","depth":5},{"id":60,"text":"\" There ' s an allegation by the acting FBI director at the time","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"that the deputy attorney general was basically trying to do an administrative coup , \"","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"he said on CBS ' s \" Face the Nation. \"","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"\" The deputy attorney general denies it .","depth":5},{"id":64,"text":"I promise your viewers the following :","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"that we will have a hearing","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"about who ' s telling the truth ,","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"what actually happened . \"","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"Mr. Graham said","depth":4},{"id":69,"text":"he was floored by the allegations","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"and will subpoena both Mr. McCabe and Mr. Rosenstein","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"if necessary .","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"\" We are going to find out what happened here ...","depth":5},{"id":73,"text":"because the underlying accusation is beyond stunning , \"","depth":5},{"id":74,"text":"he said .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":149,"left":131,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":107,"right":130,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":106,"right":32,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":78,"right":105,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":0,"right":77,"rela